detailsSection:
The System Center Configuration Manager Certification Assessment Form is designed to help evaluate your application compatibility and validate implementation of best practices for System Center Configuration Manager platform.
 
Competed Form can be submitted as part of the logo certification program and Microsoft Partner Network competency requirements. 

This tool is also recommended for Customers to evaluate third party applications.

Learn more: http://aka.ms/enterprisecloudcertified
